{"tid":1875883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[台灣]疫情中心：撤回陸配子女來台措施","createTime":"2020-02-12T05:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T05:42:17.000Z","uid":29917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"455e3a8873960c0930f2866f849b7c2561eb5fd1","tid":1875883,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"疫情中心：撤回陸配子女來台措施 防疫國人優先<br />\n陸委會昨天宣布有條件開放陸配子女引發大眾反彈，中央流行疫情指揮中心陳時中今天下午宣布，將撤回陸委會昨天宣布所有陸配子女入境規定。<br />\n<br />\n中央流行疫情指揮中心指揮官、衛福部長陳時中今天宣布，撤回陸委會公布陸配子女回台管制措施，陸配子女若不具有中華民國國籍，仍滯留在中港澳地區者，不同意入境。<br />\n<br />\n陳時中表示，防疫有三個原情，若人在台灣，醫療絕對無差別待遇，一定全力救治，不管是誰。居家檢疫、居家隔離也是無差別管理，不會因為身分而有差別。但是邊境管制必然有差別，最大原則是國人優先。在國人優先的前提下，撤回陸委會昨天的宣布，在中國台商仍有很多具有本國國籍，清明節又有一波返台祭祖等活動，若任意開放邊境，擔心防疫量能恐不足。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bonbontech.com/Blog/Detail/title/撤回陸配子女來台措施\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbonbontech.com%2FBlog%2FDetail%2Ftitle%2F%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E9%99%B8%E9%85%8D%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=451ed19a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bonbontech.com/Blog/Detail/title/撤回陸配子女來台措施</a>"},{"pid":"d98bc5927dd9c33b255b9c9584ab59ee4ee5acbd","tid":1875883,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f4ff650cf779cc5d63c73c1335e4d7cb68ce35","tid":1875883,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"俾台灣人屌得太犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac014e6d212e7e0983f10bc600fab184c1522e89","tid":1875883,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/